name: Year In Review 2021 - Spoiler Alert: We Got MARRIED!
description:
Watch this video to see the highs and lows of 2021 here at GreenerGrass! 

We’re two of the luckiest people in the world and, thanks to you, we’ve been able to share some of our exciting adventures in the sky, on the rails, and even on the roads this year here on YouTube. 

In this video, we'll revisit the year we’ve just had. We’ll give out a handful of “awards” highlighting the best (and the worst) of 2021 in all kinds of categories! 

We'll talk about the BEST Travel Experience of 2021 along with the WORST Travel Experience of 2021. We'll reveal our Travel Meals of 2021 and even share the most Disappointing Video of 2021. You'll see some of our favorite Blooper Moments. We'll share the Travel Destinations of the Year, the Best Creative Direction and Onscreen Performance. And, best of all, we'll share our Top Trip of 2021.
